<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.7.10">
<l>aṉṉamum mīṉu māmaiyu mariyu māyavem māyaṉē yaruḷāy</l>
<l>eṉṉumiṉ toṇṭark kiṉṉaruḷ puriyu miṭaventai yentaipi rāṉai</l>
<l>maṉṉumā māṭa maṅkaiyar talaivaṉ māṉavēl kaliyaṉvā yolikaḷ</l>
<l>paṉṉiya paṉuval pāṭuvār nāḷum paḻaviṉai paṟṟaṟup pārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who daily sing this [well-]crafted composition, the verses</l>
<l>By Kaliyaṉ with a proud spear, chief of those of Maṅkai</l>
<l rend="indent">with great, sturdy mansions,</l>
<l>About the lord father of Iṭaventai who gives his sweet grace</l>
<l rend="indent">to the sweet devotees who say,</l>
<l>“Our Māyaṉ who became a swan, fish, turtle, and lion! Be gracious!”</l>
<l rend="indent">they will sever the bonds of past actions.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
